<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="931200000t" end="956400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0">为追寻贤者之石的秘密</p>
<p begin="958400000t" end="999900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1">爱德与阿尔潜入了原第五研究所</p>
<p begin="1006600000t" end="1045900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2">遇到了灵魂固定在盔甲上的人们</p>
<p begin="1063800000t" end="1076600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3">战斗之中</p>
<p begin="1078900000t" end="1100300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4">听了66号的话</p>
<p begin="1102600000t" end="1123100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5">阿尔开始怀疑</p>
<p begin="1123400000t" end="1190900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6">自己或许是爱德制造出来的虚假灵魂</p>
<p begin="1247800000t" end="1265600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7">你可以起来啦</p>
<p begin="1288300000t" end="1303600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8">第五研究所呢</p>
<p begin="1305600000t" end="1313700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9">这个…</p>
<p begin="1323300000t" end="1350900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10">被人炸毁 不成形状了</p>
<p begin="1352800000t" end="1378200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11">可恶 又泡汤啦</p>
<p begin="1388400000t" end="1412400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12">啊…好痛</p>
<p begin="1417000000t" end="1440700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13">可…可恶…</p>
<p begin="1444300000t" end="1473900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14">差点就能抓住真相了</p>
<p begin="1476700000t" end="1500100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15">现在根本不是住院的时候啊</p>
<p begin="1529300000t" end="1544700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16">钢之炼金术师先生</p>
<p begin="1552900000t" end="1574000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17">我们先为无礼之举向您道歉了</p>
<p begin="1664200000t" end="1677500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18">怎么这么任性妄为呢</p>
<p begin="1682100000t" end="1705800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19">搞不好差点连命都没了</p>
<p begin="1727600000t" end="1750100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20">不要任何事情都靠自己</p>
<p begin="1754800000t" end="1767400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21">偶尔也依赖一下周围的人啊</p>
<p begin="1800700000t" end="1838400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22">你们应该更相信大人一点啊</p>
<p begin="1886500000t" end="1894200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23">完毕</p>
<p begin="1902600000t" end="1941700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24">属下言谈举止多有僭越 还请原谅</p>
<p begin="1965800000t" end="2001700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25">不…是我不好</p>
<p begin="2015800000t" end="2040400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26">刚才那一巴掌 请您处罚</p>
<p begin="2049000000t" end="2064700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27">哪有什么处罚啊</p>
<p begin="2078000000t" end="2098900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28">你们干嘛这么毕恭毕敬的</p>
<p begin="2100700000t" end="2135400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29">国家炼金术师的地位相当于军队少校嘛</p>
<p begin="2144900000t" end="2185500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30">我可不是为了地位才取得国家资格的</p>
<p begin="2193400000t" end="2216400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31">你们不用这么小心说话啦</p>
<p begin="2218800000t" end="2229500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32">哟 是么</p>
<p begin="2230200000t" end="2255100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33">呀 早知道就不费这神了</p>
<p begin="2258000000t" end="2269800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34">转变好快</p>
<p begin="2287900000t" end="2302300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35">说来阿尔呢</p>
<p begin="2304700000t" end="2347600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36">阿尔冯斯君刚刚由我铁拳教训过了</p>
<p begin="2357200000t" end="2365600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37">痛…</p>
<p begin="2385500000t" end="2423100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38">还有一顿臭骂要挨呢</p>
<p begin="2483700000t" end="2509200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39">你好 洛克贝尔义肢装备店</p>
<p begin="2526700000t" end="2534600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40">爱德？</p>
<p begin="2537000000t" end="2564400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41">你怎么会来电话 真稀奇</p>
<p begin="2567090000t" end="2591100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42">那…那个</p>
<p begin="2592500000t" end="2606900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43">虽然有点难以启齿</p>
<p begin="2608500000t" end="2636900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44">不过你能不能出差到中央市来帮我维修啊</p>
<p begin="2639200000t" end="2648100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45">出差？</p>
<p begin="2651500000t" end="2675700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46">呃…那个右臂啊</p>
<p begin="2680200000t" end="2693300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47">虽然手指还能动</p>
<p begin="2693700000t" end="2713900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48">但是手臂完全抬不起来了</p>
<p begin="2771700000t" end="2786400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49">果然有问题啊</p>
<p begin="2793100000t" end="2809100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50">不不 我自言自语呢</p>
<p begin="2820000000t" end="2841900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51">你做了什么让它不能动了</p>
<p begin="2875200000t" end="2888300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52">跟人大打了一架</p>
<p begin="2893700000t" end="2937300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53">你又来了 你到底想怎么折腾我的机械铠啊</p>
<p begin="2992900000t" end="3002800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54">喂喂</p>
<p begin="3009700000t" end="3023800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55">温莉…小姐？</p>
<p begin="3030700000t" end="3042300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56">真拿你没办法</p>
<p begin="3044600000t" end="3056400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57">你在中央市的哪里？</p>
<p begin="3074000000t" end="3097300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58">你今天怎么这么温柔…</p>
<p begin="3107800000t" end="3125300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59">不 没什么</p>
<p begin="3151900000t" end="3165000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60">不好意思 麻烦你了</p>
<p begin="3169800000t" end="3184100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61">嗯 回见</p>
<p begin="3211500000t" end="3221700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62">打电话给女朋友？</p>
<p begin="3222100000t" end="3242900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63">鬼才有女朋友啊</p>
<p begin="3259500000t" end="3276500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64">什么嘛 真没劲</p>
<p begin="3279200000t" end="3296200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65">我在你这年纪的时候…</p>
<p begin="3296400000t" end="3303000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66">咦</p>
<p begin="3312200000t" end="3332100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67">做什么呢 在那角落里</p>
<p begin="3343000000t" end="3357500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68">喂 阿尔</p>
<p begin="3367800000t" end="3376100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69">哥哥</p>
<p begin="3381900000t" end="3394000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70">不回房间吗</p>
<p begin="3462300000t" end="3480300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71">不 没事</p>
<p begin="3481700000t" end="3491600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72">你先走吧</p>
<p begin="3716900000t" end="3725300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73">拜拜</p>
<p begin="3782000000t" end="3814600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74">其实是你哥制造的盔甲人偶吧</p>
<p begin="3912700000t" end="3931100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75">屁股好痛</p>
<p begin="3935200000t" end="3960500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76">爱德他们竟然能忍受这种长途车</p>
<p begin="3993800000t" end="4036000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77">说是西口立了标记 一看就知道的</p>
<p begin="4063600000t" end="4080700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78">阿姆斯特朗少校</p>
<p begin="4100900000t" end="4123000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79">温莉小姐</p>
<p begin="4145200000t" end="4161900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80">艾尔利克那对笨兄弟呢</p>
<p begin="4183600000t" end="4196900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81">其实…</p>
<p begin="4260300000t" end="4275000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82">爱德他…住院了？</p>
<p begin="4307100000t" end="4327800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83">好…好快啊</p>
<p begin="4332600000t" end="4361100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84">你是打算收加急费吧</p>
<p begin="4378900000t" end="4415800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85">但是 因为我没好好维修</p>
<p begin="4416800000t" end="4430700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86">机械铠才会坏掉</p>
<p begin="4441300000t" end="4456300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87">让你受这么重的伤吧</p>
<p begin="4496900000t" end="4523100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88">这…这不是温莉的错啦</p>
<p begin="4527900000t" end="4559400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89">说到底都是因为我胡乱使用嘛</p>
<p begin="4560200000t" end="4588900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90">你的维修每次都很完美啊</p>
<p begin="4592900000t" end="4629700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91">他没发现我忘记上螺丝了？</p>
<p begin="4634500000t" end="4653600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92">而且也可以说因为右手坏掉</p>
<p begin="4653900000t" end="4679600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93">我才没有伤得更重嘛</p>
<p begin="4685100000t" end="4704300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94">别放在心上啦 好不好</p>
<p begin="4710500000t" end="4726800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95">这么说万事OK？</p>
<p begin="4736100000t" end="4775500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96">那 这就来谈谈出差维修的事吧</p>
<p begin="4779500000t" end="4800100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97">当然要收加急费哦</p>
<p begin="4841100000t" end="4854200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98">牛奶没喝</p>
<p begin="4877800000t" end="4897100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99">我不喜欢喝牛奶</p>
<p begin="4899300000t" end="4937700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100">就因为你这样才永远是个豆丁啦</p>
<p begin="4938300000t" end="4970500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101">少啰嗦 不喜欢就是不喜欢</p>
<p begin="4971700000t" end="5005700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102">你太任性了 爱德华·艾尔利克</p>
<p begin="5012200000t" end="5031100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103">小孩子都要喝牛奶</p>
<p begin="5033500000t" end="5053200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104">不喝牛奶找不到女朋友哦</p>
<p begin="5071100000t" end="5080500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105">阿尔？</p>
<p begin="5160700000t" end="5189600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106">阿尔那家伙 最近怪怪的</p>
<p begin="5211100000t" end="5221000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107">怪怪的？</p>
<p begin="5240390000t" end="5261600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108">好像有什么心事</p>
<p begin="5403200000t" end="5444400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109">你其实是你哥制造的盔甲人偶吧</p>
<p begin="5449100000t" end="5474400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110">承认吧 这样会舒服些</p>
<p begin="5556500000t" end="5574700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111">好 修好了</p>
<p begin="5583500000t" end="5594900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112">太好了</p>
<p begin="5599100000t" end="5635400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113">总算修好了 谢啦</p>
<p begin="5640300000t" end="5651200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114">不客气</p>
<p begin="5670400000t" end="5681900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115">哟 爱德</p>
<p begin="5687400000t" end="5712600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116">听说你带女人到病房卿卿我我？</p>
<p begin="5731800000t" end="5760000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117">只是机械铠维修师而已啦</p>
<p begin="5771400000t" end="5788800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118">原来你泡了个维修师啊</p>
<p begin="5802200000t" end="5827500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119">强词夺理啊</p>
<p begin="5840700000t" end="5860400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120">我是马斯·修兹 多关照</p>
<p begin="5861900000t" end="5878700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121">我是温莉·洛克贝尔</p>
<p begin="5885900000t" end="5909000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122">没问题吗 翘班跑出来</p>
<p begin="5916000000t" end="5928300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123">不用担心</p>
<p begin="5935000000t" end="5949400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124">我让谢丝卡留下来加班了</p>
<p begin="5959000000t" end="5972300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125">你魔鬼啊</p>
<p begin="5977300000t" end="6018900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126">说来 你们很快就可以解除警卫了</p>
<p begin="6021400000t" end="6032300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127">真的吗</p>
<p begin="6037300000t" end="6048500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128">警卫…</p>
<p begin="6053000000t" end="6089600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129">我说你到底遇上了什么危险啊</p>
<p begin="6102500000t" end="6127400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130">不 这个…嗯怎么说呢</p>
<p begin="6151400000t" end="6176300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131">没…没什么大不了的啦</p>
<p begin="6253800000t" end="6297100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132">是么 反正再怎么问你们也不肯说的</p>
<p begin="6322700000t" end="6334700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133">那明天见</p>
<p begin="6348500000t" end="6369600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134">我要去找今天的住处了</p>
<p begin="6374700000t" end="6406000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135">怎么 要不你住我家好了</p>
<p begin="6412700000t" end="6419500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136">但是…</p>
<p begin="6419700000t" end="6433000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137">别客气啦</p>
<p begin="6434100000t" end="6451600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138">我老婆孩子都会很开心的</p>
<p begin="6451700000t" end="6457000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139">这…</p>
<p begin="6457300000t" end="6470200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140">好 就这么办</p>
<p begin="6470600000t" end="6484400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141">那个…我说</p>
<p begin="6484800000t" end="6496900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142">来来 走吧</p>
<p begin="6510200000t" end="6534500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143">等等～</p>
<p begin="6608300000t" end="6636100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144">爱莉希娅 生日快乐</p>
<p begin="6673000000t" end="6707400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145">请问修兹先生 这是…？</p>
<p begin="6709300000t" end="6729600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146">你总算发觉了</p>
<p begin="6733300000t" end="6759200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147">今天是爱莉希娅的生日呀</p>
<p begin="6764200000t" end="6777500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148">生日呀</p>
<p begin="6801800000t" end="6825500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149">今年几岁了 爱莉希娅</p>
<p begin="6828900000t" end="6836000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150">两…</p>
