<p begin="6868900000t" end="6884100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152">好…好…</p>
<p begin="6886800000t" end="6910900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle153">好可爱</p>
<p begin="7003400000t" end="7035400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle154">我跟他们从小就在一起了</p>
<p begin="7037400000t" end="7051400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle155">简直就像兄弟姐妹一样</p>
<p begin="7067400000t" end="7085400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle156">那两个家伙肯定让你操了不少心吧</p>
<p begin="7089400000t" end="7101400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle157">就是呀</p>
<p begin="7104400000t" end="7120400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle158">好不容易偶尔回来一次</p>
<p begin="7122400000t" end="7137400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle159">结果胳膊又整个散架</p>
<p begin="7186400000t" end="7220400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle160">被叫出来 爱德又是身受重伤</p>
<p begin="7223400000t" end="7240400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle161">阿尔也那么消沉</p>
<p begin="7264400000t" end="7303400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle162">但是 无论发生什么他们都不会告诉我</p>
<p begin="7311400000t" end="7328400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle163">离开里森堡的时候也是</p>
<p begin="7352400000t" end="7373400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle164">因为他们觉得没必要跟你说吧</p>
<p begin="7394400000t" end="7439400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle165">他们一定认为即便不说温莉也能理解</p>
<p begin="7477400000t" end="7517400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle166">可是 有些事情不说就没法传达给别人</p>
<p begin="7537400000t" end="7554400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle167">没办法啊</p>
<p begin="7571400000t" end="7605400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle168">比起言语 男人这种生物更乐于用行动来表达意志吧</p>
<p begin="7614400000t" end="7657400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle169">遇到痛苦的事情 都尽量不让周围人来分担</p>
<p begin="7661400000t" end="7680400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle170">也不想让别人担心</p>
<p begin="7685400000t" end="7695400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle171">所以才不说出来</p>
<p begin="7727400000t" end="7760400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle172">不过 等这对兄弟向你诉苦</p>
<p begin="7773400000t" end="7803400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle173">到时候你再完全包容理解他们</p>
<p begin="7811400000t" end="7825400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle174">这样不就行了吗</p>
<p begin="7858400000t" end="7882400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle175">爱莉希娅 一起玩儿吧</p>
<p begin="7886400000t" end="7897400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle176">让我下去吧</p>
<p begin="7900400000t" end="7913400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle177">好啊</p>
