<p begin="8142400000t" end="8155400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle184">真的没关系吗</p>
<p begin="8159400000t" end="8192400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle185">待在中央市这段期间 你可以一直住这里呀</p>
<p begin="8195400000t" end="8215400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle186">不能这么麻烦你们啦</p>
<p begin="8244400000t" end="8263400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle187">看她这么黏你</p>
