<p begin="8328400000t" end="8358400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle190">路上小心 要早点回来哦</p>
<p begin="8369400000t" end="8387400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle191">看来今晚也要住这里了哦</p>
<p begin="8427400000t" end="8450400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle192">好像真的多了个妹妹 好开心</p>
<p begin="8521400000t" end="8554400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle193">今天也出现了 这鬼东西</p>
<p begin="8572400000t" end="8603400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle194">因为哥哥还是肉身</p>
<p begin="8618400000t" end="8631400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle195">所以一定要喝哦</p>
<p begin="8652400000t" end="8672400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle196">不喜欢就是不喜欢</p>
<p begin="8678400000t" end="8698400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle197">别看这样 我也有长高哦</p>
<p begin="8701400000t" end="8724400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle198">可是个人都说我矮</p>
<p begin="8738400000t" end="8754400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle199">还是阿尔好</p>
