<p begin="9172400000t" end="9212400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle213">哥哥 你之前不是说有件事害怕得不敢跟我说吗</p>
<p begin="9221400000t" end="9232400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle214">难道你要说的是</p>
<p begin="9239400000t" end="9268400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle215">其实我的灵魂和记忆</p>
<p begin="9272400000t" end="9306400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle216">全部都是捏造出来的假货吗</p>
<p begin="9342400000t" end="9388400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle217">温莉还有婆婆 也都是合伙骗我的吧</p>
<p begin="9400400000t" end="9421400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle218">你说话啊 哥哥</p>
