<p begin="9525400000t" end="9560400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle220">你想说的话都说完了吗</p>
<p begin="9619400000t" end="9628400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle221">是吗</p>
<p begin="9734400000t" end="9741400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle222">爱德</p>
<p begin="9752400000t" end="9760400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle223">爱德</p>
