<p begin="12882400000t" end="12920400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle303">这里还有其他伊修瓦尔幸存者吗</p>
<p begin="12923400000t" end="12940400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle304">哦 有啊</p>
<p begin="12946400000t" end="12985400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle305">虽然这里满是煤味 不过住起来还算是不错</p>
<p begin="12988400000t" end="13048400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle306">「世中处处皆是吾神伊修瓦拉的胸怀」嘛</p>
<p begin="13066400000t" end="13085400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle307">是吗</p>
<p begin="13097400000t" end="13111400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle308">别乱动啦</p>
<p begin="13116400000t" end="13143400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle309">你可是浑身是伤从下水道里漂过来的</p>
<p begin="13232000000t" end="13264400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle310">请问 我的右臂还在吗</p>
<p begin="13268400000t" end="13288400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle311">嗯 还在哦</p>
<p begin="13321400000t" end="13349400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle312">真惊人啊 这纹身</p>
<p begin="13365400000t" end="13435400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle313">嗯 那是亲人给我的重要羁绊</p>
<p begin="14385400000t" end="14413400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle314">挚友成了战友</p>
<p begin="14417400000t" end="14446400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle315">守护在身边成了理所当然的事</p>
<p begin="14453400000t" end="14472400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle316">即使曾经畅谈过的未来</p>
<p begin="14476400000t" end="14498400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle317">如今已染上铅尘</p>
<p begin="14506400000t" end="14530400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle318">挚友却依然相伴左右</p>
<p begin="14544400000t" end="14582400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle319">下集 钢之炼金术师 Fullmetel Alchemist</p>
<p begin="14585000000t" end="14612400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle320">第10话 各自的前途</p>
<p begin="14623400000t" end="14639400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle321">理所当然的存在</p>
<p begin="14640400000t" end="14667400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle322">那是无可替代的宝物</p>
